sequenceDiagram
    participant W as Workload
    participant V as Verifier
    participant CA as Credential<br/>Authority
    note over W, CA: Credential Acquisition Phase
    W->>+W: Generate Key
    W->>+W: Create Evidence (Quote)<br/>including Key PoP
    W->>+V: Request<br/> Attestation Results<br/>with Quote as Evidence
    V->>+V: Compute Attestation Results<br/>from Evidence
    V->>+W: Attestation Results
    W->>+W: Compute Credential Attributes<br/>from Attestation Results
    W->>+CA: Credential Request
    CA->>+CA: Convert Attestation Results<br/>to Credential Attributes
    CA->>+CA: Create and Sign a Credential<br/>from Credential Request<br/>and Credential Attributes
    CA->>+W: Credential
